Subject: [PATCH] Apply patch `st-dracula-0.8.2.diff`

The `st-dracula-0.8.2.diff` conflicted with the `st-alpha-0.8.2.diff`
patch when trying to `git apply`, so this is a diff that resolves that
conflict.

